{"id": "1420100832774459442", "channel_id": "1420092491125755985", "type": 0, "author_id": "1213364721328332840", "author_name": "akalanden", "author_bot": false, "content": "依稀记得好像有说还有一个SP来着，介于在攻略组看到的东西，我说一个SP汀克特", "timestamp": "2025-09-23T17:33:42.731000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
