{"id": "1420101292088360961", "channel_id": "1420092491125755985", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "We’ve tried some of these and they can be fun, but we can’t afford them at the moment. Our creators pulled consecutive overtime making this content, ended up exhausted, their health suffered, and the quality of work was affected. As the producer, I need to strike a balance so we can serve everyone better over the long term.", "timestamp": "2025-09-23T17:35:32.240000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["291661719262986240"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🥹", "emoji_id": null, "count": 13}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}, {"emoji": "🩷", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "OK", "emoji_id": "1400771749506715668", "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1420100382461530162", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1420102048648532130", "channel_id": "1420092491125755985", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "Since most of the artists are active on Weibo in China and, as far as I know, most don’t have X accounts, I’m sorry but I can’t provide them.", "timestamp": "2025-09-23T17:38:32.618000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["877511774834917427"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1420097067174592523", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1420102182707138671", "channel_id": "1420092491125755985", "type": 0, "author_id": "1156964372397178960", "author_name": "taoi002", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@633215996508766229>鑰令的設計方向是否遇到瓶頸?目前大約有九成「新鑰令」都被綁定在新角色的專屬效果上，這樣的設計明顯過於單調，鑰令的初衷應該是提供不同隊伍更多元組合的可能，讓玩家能依據隊伍配置、戰鬥需求與策略來選擇，而不是被綁死在某個角色上。建議鑰令的設計應往更宏觀方向發展，讓鑰令能成為「隊伍戰略的選擇」，而不是只對「某個角色效果的提升」。", "timestamp": "2025-09-23T17:39:04.580000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1420102643967332362", "channel_id": "1420092491125755985", "type": 0, "author_id": "557599119401811978", "author_name": "heikwok", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@633215996508766229>  \n認真想問一下，傷害型角色有考慮加強或調整功能方面的設計嗎\n就那些純傷主C，新的姑且先不說，舊的在數值上也跟不上怪物膨脹\n現在有不少輔助當主C通過各種機制完勝純C，而且純C沒有輔助能力且傷害跟不上版本導致出現失業問題，本身沒有什麼特殊機制，比較綁定數值深化提升，整體造價也相對較高，策略方面的實用度卻完全比不上其他類型角色的設計\n\n另外抽牌過牌產牌的角色有沒有考慮提供適當的算力調和豁免，比如給萊克前三張牌免算力調和之類的，主要是算力調和很影響這類角色的發揮\n甚至簡單點只是用蘿坦，為了疊滿靈塑的臨時終傷效果以獲取最大收益，不得不囤牌打一波爆發，卻總是遇到被算力調和卡牌的情況，整體輸出平平無奇甚至不如常駐C，感覺沒必要受限於此", "timestamp": "2025-09-23T17:40:54.553000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "S_OK", "emoji_id": "1400771749506715668", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1420102646739501257", "channel_id": "1420092491125755985", "type": 19, "author_id": "877511774834917427", "author_name": ".cnork", "author_bot": false, "content": "How can one then see their work?", "timestamp": "2025-09-23T17:40:55.214000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1420102048648532130", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
