{"id": "1420103030275182602", "channel_id": "1420092491125755985", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "我们确实目前采用了钥令跟某个角色更相关的能力设计思路，因为通用而强大钥令工具已经非常多，暂时不适合更多。", "timestamp": "2025-09-23T17:42:26.656000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1156964372397178960"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1420102182707138671", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1420103356902408224", "channel_id": "1420092491125755985", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "对于玩法体验我们始终在想办法。之前日本版本确实占据了许多玩法设计师的时间，今后我们会有更多机会来审视已有问题。", "timestamp": "2025-09-23T17:43:44.530000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["557599119401811978"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1420102643967332362", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1420103520601903275", "channel_id": "1420092491125755985", "type": 0, "author_id": "944524613168279553", "author_name": "ena04564", "author_bot": false, "content": "貓我想問一下你們有考慮星辰篇困難難度（特別是第一章）的怪血量可以下調嗎，個人覺得就通關配隊第一章不玩融朵過關有點太極限了", "timestamp": "2025-09-23T17:44:23.559000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
